---
import RocketIcon from "./icons/rocketIcon.astro"
import DiscordIcon from "./icons/discordIcon.astro"
---
<section id="sobre-nosotros" class="relative flex flex-col pb-24 px-10 sm:px-10 scroll-mt-36 justify-center items-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Título -->
    <header class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center dark:text-gray-300 text-gray-800 my-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-Chakra font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#7ADBF7] via-[#4AB5E4] to-[#2A6BA9] bg-clip-text text-transparent">Sobre GlaciarMC</h1>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row mb-5 max-w-5xl justify-center items-center">
        
        <div class=" p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white font-Chakra mb-3 text-center">Una experiencia única</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-center w-full sm:w-2xl [&>strong]:text-sky-400">
                <strong>GlaciarMC</strong> es un servidor de Minecraft que busca ofrecer <strong>aventuras inolvidables</strong>, amistades nuevas y modalidades emocionantes diseñadas con pasión y dedicación.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl w-full grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 z-10 gap-5">

        <div class="group overflow-hidden relative border border-gray-500/20 hover:border-gray-500/40 transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br rounded-2xl from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-cyan-900/10 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <i class="group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 fa-solid fa-rocket text-3xl text-[#7ADBF7]"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white font-Chakra group-hover:text-[#5A9FD6] transition-colors duration-300">Modalidades</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 z-10">Disfruta de Survival, SkyBlock, Minijuegos y mucho más, con características únicas desarrolladas por nuestro equipo.</p>
            <i class="absolute fa-solid fa-rocket text-7xl text-[#5A9FD6] -bottom-2 -z-10 right-[-10px] -rotate-90 group-hover:scale-115 transform group-hover:translate-x-[-5px] group-hover:translate-y-[-5px] transition-all duration-500"></i>
        </div>
        
        <div class="group overflow-hidden relative border border-gray-500/20 hover:border-gray-500/40 transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br rounded-2xl from-sky-50 to-indigo-50 dark:from-sky-900/20 dark:to-indigo-900/10 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-people-group text-3xl text-[#4AB5E4]"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white font-Chakra group-hover:text-[#5A9FD6] transition-colors duration-300">Comunidad</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 z-10">Únete a miles de jugadores en una comunidad activa, amigable y diversa donde siempre hay algo nuevo que descubrir.</p>
            <i class="absolute fa-solid fa-people-group text-7xl text-[#5A9FD6] -bottom-2 -z-10 right-[-10px] -rotate-20 group-hover:scale-115 transform group-hover:translate-x-[-5px] group-hover:translate-y-[-5px] transition-all duration-500"></i>
        </div>
        
        <div class="group overflow-hidden relative border border-gray-500/20 hover:border-gray-500/40 transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br rounded-2xl from-indigo-50 to-blue-50 dark:from-indigo-900/20 dark:to-blue-900/10 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-3xl text-[#2A6BA9]"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white font-Chakra group-hover:text-[#5A9FD6] transition-colors duration-300">Seguridad</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 z-10">Cuenta con un equipo de moderación activo las 24/7 para garantizar una experiencia de juego segura y libre de problemas.</p>
            <i class="absolute fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-7xl text-[#5A9FD6] -bottom-1.5 -z-10 right-[-10px] rotate-20 group-hover:scale-115 transform group-hover:translate-x-[-5px] group-hover:translate-y-[-5px] transition-all duration-500"></i>
        </div>
        
        <div class="group overflow-hidden relative border border-gray-500/20 hover:border-gray-500/40 transition-all duration-300 bg-gradient-to-br rounded-2xl from-blue-50 to-sky-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-sky-900/10 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days text-3xl text-[#5A9FD6]"></i>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white font-Chakra group-hover:text-[#5A9FD6] transition-colors duration-300">Eventos</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 z-10">Participa en eventos semanales con premios exclusivos, competencias y actividades especiales para toda la comunidad.</p>
            <i class="absolute fa-solid fa-calendar-days text-7xl text-[#5A9FD6] bottom-2 -z-10 right-[-10px] rotate-20 group-hover:scale-115 transform group-hover:translate-x-[-5px] transition-all duration-500"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>
